\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces McNemar's exact test (one-sided) vs.\ baseline ($n{=}122$). Bonferroni threshold: $\alpha {=}0.0071$ (7 comparisons). Only Llama Guard survives Bonferroni correction; \textsc  {Parse}\xspace  approaches it with the largest effect size ($h{=}{-}0.245$) and adequate power. parse\_dc = parse\_domain\_conditional.}}{6}{table.caption.14}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{tab:stats}{{2}{6}{McNemar's exact test (one-sided) vs.\ baseline ($n{=}122$). Bonferroni threshold: $\alpha {=}0.0071$ (7 comparisons). Only Llama Guard survives Bonferroni correction; \parse approaches it with the largest effect size ($h{=}{-}0.245$) and adequate power. parse\_dc = parse\_domain\_conditional}{table.caption.14}{}}
